link: Harry J. Smith, Table of n, a(n) for n = 2..20000
program: (PARI) { default(realprecision, 20080); x=exp(1)^4/10; for (n=2, 20000, d=floor(x); x=(x-d)*10; write("b092426.txt", n, " ", d)); } \\ _Harry J. Smith_, Jun 22 2009
